import {
  FormControl,
  FormLabel,
  FormErrorMessage,
  FormHelperText,
  Box,
  Center
} from '@chakra-ui/react'
function Boxer () {
    <Center>
      <Box bg='#F0FD1F' w='30%' h='500px'  p={4} color = 'white' borderRadius = 'lg' alignItems='center'>
      <FormControl>
        <Center>
        <FormLabel color='red' >Add Sundae</FormLabel>
        </Center>
        <Center>
        <FormHelperText>Here is some other text</FormHelperText>
        </Center>
      </FormControl>
      </Box>
      </Center>
}

export default Boxer;
